<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Span on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/span/</link><description>Recent content in Span on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/span/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::span Error — Span Bounds Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/span-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/span-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-stdspan-error--span-bounds-fix"&gt;[Solution] C++ std::span Error — Span Bounds Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;std::span&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when accessing elements beyond the span&amp;rsquo;s bounds, when the span dangles (references destroyed data), or when a span is constructed with incorrect size information. &lt;code&gt;std::span::at()&lt;/code&gt; throws &lt;code&gt;std::out_of_range&lt;/code&gt;, while &lt;code&gt;operator[]&lt;/code&gt; has undefined behavior.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="why-stdspan-errors-occurs"&gt;Why std::span Errors Occurs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes include accessing indices beyond span size, span outliving the underlying container, constructing a span with a size larger than the actual data, and using &lt;code&gt;static_extent&lt;/code&gt; that doesn&amp;rsquo;t match the actual data.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] ObservabilityException — Spring Observability Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/spring-observability/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/spring-observability/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="observabilityexception--spring-observability-fix"&gt;ObservabilityException — Spring Observability Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;ObservabilityException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when Spring Observability (Micrometer Tracing) fails to create a span. This typically occurs when the tracing backend is unavailable or misconfigured.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common message:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ObservabilityException: Span creation failed&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ObservabilityException: No tracer configured&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: No tracing backend configured&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Micrometer Tracing needs Brave or OpenTelemetry&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Tracing backend unavailable&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Zipkin/Jaeger not running&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Configuration mismatch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-add-micrometer-tracing-dependencies"&gt;Fix 1: Add Micrometer Tracing dependencies&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;io.micrometer&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;micrometer-tracing-bridge-brave&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;io.zipkin.reporter2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;zipkin-reporter-brave&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-configure-tracing"&gt;Fix 2: Configure tracing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;management&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;tracing&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;sampling&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;probability&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1.0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;zipkin&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;tracing&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;endpoint&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-disable-tracing-if-not-needed"&gt;Fix 3: Disable tracing if not needed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;management&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;tracing&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;enabled&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/spring-cloud-config/ — ConfigDataException&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/spring-bean/ — NoSuchBeanDefinitionException&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/spring-cloud-gateway/ — ResponseStatusException: 502&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>